<br>
You work together as a team, either for laughs or to Raid, but as a unity.  You cant have Jo Whoever make it from level 1 to 60 in a week and wonder why the rest of the guild who are still stuck at level 10 and ask why cant we raid ToV.    <br>
<br>
Now I dont want to say that this style is the only style for a guild, but those guilds doing raids on a regular basis and want to be successful, this is absolutely true.  <br>
<br>
And for those Rare guilds that are together just to hang with good friends, God Bless you, Havent meet any yet, but you can pretty much do anything you want and the members just wont seem to mind much.  Let the good times roll.<br>
